pulse ambeurdep on xetra eur  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description andersen  martini as am is a denmarkbased company engaged in the dealing of new and used cars as well as in provision of automotive services for consumers and businesses it is engaged both in direct activities and partnerships with leasing and rental companies the company offers and services both passenger and commercial vehicles of brands such as opel kia peugeot fiat saab cadillac and corvette it operates in the urban area of copenhagen via customer centers in amager ballerup gladsaxe glostrup lyngby soeborg and taastrup it is also engaged in the wholesale of used cars the portfolio of services comprises several types of leasing car repair roadside assistance winter safety checks rust treatment and tire storage all of which can be booked online the company’s largest shareholder is helmsman holding aps » full overview of ambeurdep company address andersen  martini as agenavej greve      company web links home page officers  directors name compensation henning hurdum  peter hansen  erik justesen  jan asmussen  jesper hansen  » more officers  directors andersen  martini as news briefandersen  martini fy ebitda up at dkk  million mar   » more ambeurdep news related topics stocksstock screenerauto vehicles parts  service retailers andersen  martini as  company spotlight profile warning this site has features that require javascript watch andersen  martini as sector automobiles and other motor vehicles region denmark   nasdaq omx copenhagen amb ♣ request investor kit view contact details news  analysis featured company value and income trust plc glasgow gb value  income trust plc is an investment trust which is designed for both institutional and private investors whose shares you may also be interested in tekla healthcare investors boston ma us tekla healthcare investors hqh is a diversified closedend healthcare fund traded on the new yo