s a lot of product lines which means that there is often a need to measure on the individual product line so that you can quickly intervene if the reality differs from the plan the company uses an erp system which is specifically aimed at the automotive industry a solid tool for managing daily transactions but like many other erp systems it’s almost as hard for budgeting and management reporting from quarterly reporting to monthly reporting the solution to the reporting task became toolpack “the decision to acquire toolpack did not take long” says economist martin ørbæk nielsen and continues “the product had the facilities we requested and toolpack consultants appeared professional and competent they were ready to make a  percent integration of toolpack with our erp system the latter was a crucial condition because we did not want to make manual data transfers with all the errors and the time it causes ” in less time than previously it was time to prepare the summary quarterly report martin ørbæk nielsen can now using toolpack service all budget managers with detailed monthly financial reports budgets and realized numbers are gathered in toolpack and the individual budget manager can even extract the reports directly in excel we all know excel the budget managers at andersen  martini is excited that toolpack is based on excel “we all know excel in advance so we only needed time to get to know the new toolpack features” says martin ørbæk nielsen “at first i was a bit concerned about whether excel could handle the large amounts of data but it did not prove to be a problem” continues the chief financial officer “by using excel we also benefit from all the new features that microsoft develops in addition all new employees we employ in sales and administration already acquainted with excel it’s the big advantage of toolpack ” a solution for financial managers martin ørbæk nielsen may notice that the people behind toolpack have a financial background “toolpack has been designed and developed by finance managers for finance managers – it is clearly visible” says martin ørbæk nielsen saying “the entire way you work with the product exactly matches the way an economist is thinking” optimeot april customer cases del denne historie vælg din platform top  andersen  martini as reviews  read customer service reviews of amdk trustpilot reviews andersen  martini as reviews great  from     reviews on trustpilot asking for reviews not inviting to our knowledge andersen  martini as asks its customers to review their experience on trustpilot to our knowledge this company doesn’t invite its customers to write reviews on trustpilot read more show rating distribution hide rating distribution andersen  martini as reviews great   reviews details reviews ◆ about ◆ voice your opinion review andersen  martini as now roll over stars then click to rate tap stars to rate  star bad – unacceptable experience unreasonable and rude conduct  stars poor – an inadequate experience with a lot of friction  stars average – acceptable experience but with some friction  stars great – decent treatment and very little friction  stars excellent – no reservations i would recommend this company to anyone review company filter reviews star rating  ★  ★  ★  ★  ★ language all languages  dansk  english  norsk  svenska  nederlands  deutsch  frysk  polski  frederik hostruppedersen ordrup dk  reviews published  hours ago frederik hostruppedersen was invited to write this review by andersen  martini as learn more verified order frederik hostruppedersen was invited to write this review by andersen  martini as learn more super service super service useful share facebook google twitter pagesreviewstackedshowmorezero only the latest review will count in the companys trustscore pagesreviewstackedhidestackzero lars busk preheim  review published  days ago lars busk preheim was invited to write this review by andersen  martini as learn more verified order lars busk preheim was invited to