d cars which can jeopardize innocent lives who knowswhy the salesman started lying and backed out of the contract we negotiated and shook hands onafter complaining to his supervisor he told me he will try to find out what was the problem with the car and get back to me while in the meantime he’s going to search for a car with similar options after waiting almost a week for an answer and a new offer i decided to call to find out about the status of my complaint the answer was his salesman was in holiday for the upcoming weeks and he couldn’t find more info about the car i informed him that i found that the car has been registered tuesday the th of march two days after my visit at your dealership with the following number plates bk over the phone he also told me he doesn’t have any offers for me customer service is nonexisting at andersen and martini since i wrote  other complaints directed to sales operation manager and andersen martini ceo both complaints have not been answered to this daya very disappointed and disrespected customergelu laurentiu useful share facebook google twitter reply from andersen  martini as published thursday april   dear mr motorga laurentiuwe are sorry about the situation which basically is very simplewe acknowledge the fact that you wanted to buy the particular car in question however you never confirmed neither did you sign the sales contractaccording to our policy a car is not sold until the contract has been signed and since another customer wanted to buy and sign the car was sold to the latterunfortunately our salesman did not tell you the true reason why you could not buy the car namely that the car was sold to another customer a full legitimate reason as to why he could not sell the car to younotwithstanding that our branch manager offered you to find a simelar car however i understand you and he did not come to termsmay we suggest you come to our shop again and we shall offer you a good deal for another carbest regardspeter hansena